response.overview: The Wonder Stuff perform their classic 1989 album HUP for the first time. Shot with 8 cameras at Birmingham Academy to a sold out home town crowd. This is the whole show including extra tracks performed on the night. Track List: 30 Years In The Bathroom - Radio Ass Kiss - Them, Big Oak Trees - Golden Green - Cartoon Boyfriend - Unfaithful - Piece of Sky - Let’s Be Other People - Don’t Let Me Down, Gently - Can’t Shape Up - Room 410 - Good Night Though - Gimme Some Truth - Inside You - Circlesquare - On The Ropes - Last Second of the Minute - Mission Drive - The Size of a Cow - Unbearable - Ten Trenches Deep
response.title: The Wonder Stuff: Hup Live
